            "text_Uidqpe": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p><strong>Natural Hevea Rubber Baby Teethers</strong><br/><br/>Available in 4 charming designs — <strong>Watermelon, Bunny, Carrot and Koala Bear</strong> — thoughtfully created to soothe teething babies while supporting safe, natural play.</p><h3>Key Features</h3><p>✓ Made from <strong>100% Natural Hevea Rubber</strong><br/><br/>✓ <strong>CE, UKCA & EN71 Certified</strong> for safety and quality<br/><br/>✓ <strong>BPA, PVC & Phthalate Free</strong><br/><br/>✓ <strong>Hypoallergenic</strong> and gentle on sensitive gums<br/><br/>✓ Colored using <strong>natural plant pigments</strong> with <strong>no harmful chemical fixatives</strong><br/><br/>✓ Easy to clean and designed for everyday use</p><h3>Why Parents Love Natural Rubber Teethers</h3><p>🌿 <strong>Environmentally Friendly</strong><br/><br/>Made from a renewable, sustainable resource that is kinder to the planet.</p><p>🦷 <strong>Soft & Flexible</strong><br/><br/>Naturally soft texture provides gentle relief for sore, sensitive gums.</p><p>✨ <strong>Natural Antibacterial Properties</strong><br/><br/>Helps resist the growth of germs and bacteria for a more hygienic teething experience.</p><p>💪 <strong>Durable & Long-Lasting</strong><br/><br/>Designed to withstand chewing while maintaining comfort and quality.</p><p>♻️ <strong>Biodegradable</strong><br/><br/>An eco-conscious choice that naturally breaks down over time without harming nature.</p><p>🧼 <strong>Easy to Clean</strong><br/><br/>Simple, practical cleaning makes daily use effortless for busy parents.</p><p><strong>Safe, soothing and inspired by nature — our Hevea rubber teethers help comfort little ones through every stage of teething.</strong> 💚</p>",
